      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>A bill to prevent congressional reapportionment distortions by requiring that, in the questionnaires used in the taking of any decennial census of population, a checkbox or other similar option be included for respondents to indicate citizenship status or lawful presence in the United States.</title>
